<item>
            <title>[CXF-5404] NPE in AtomPojoProvider when no content (or content is empty)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-5404</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using the AtomPojoProvider with JAX-RS - the library bombs with an NPE (embedded in a ClientErrorException) if using JAXB annotated content objects - but no content is provided in the entry.  It also NPE&apos;s if the content element is present but contains no XML (although this is a slightly dubious Atom document at this point).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Returning &quot;null&quot; would be a much better result in this case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
